BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560 Td (- It is cost-effective and fast for short case files.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 545 Td (- It performed well on the supplied corpus.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530 Td (- The files are small, so whole-document embeddings preserved useful context.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 515 Td (- Larger embeddings bought margin but not enough accuracy gain to justify the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 500 Td (  higher cost for this use case.) Tj ET
