BT /F1 10 Tf 54 466 Td ("I benchmarked whole-document versus paragraph chunks and smaller versus larger) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 453 Td (embedding models. Because these case files are short, chunking actually hurt:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 440 Td (it removed context that helped identify red herrings. So I chose whole-document) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 427 Td (embeddings with text-embedding-3-small.") Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 396 Td (Generation and retrieval-assist model: gpt-4o-mini) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 366 Td (Used for:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 353 Td (- Query expansion.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 338 Td (- Candidate relevance grading.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 323 Td (- Final investigation report generation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 300 Td (Why:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 287 Td (- Strong enough for structured reasoning and summarization.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 272 Td (- Lower cost and latency than a larger model.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 257 Td (- Appropriate for a small interactive investigation tool.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 224 Td (Judge model: gpt-4o) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 194 Td (Used only in evaluation, not in the production request path.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 173 Td (Why:) Tj ET
